data.description: Built in 2005, this single story home is centrally located with easy access to all of the amenities Aberdeen has to offer.  The home features 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, hardi plank siding, skylights, recessed lighting & laminate flooring.  The primary bedroom has a walk in closet and attached full bath.  The attached 2 car garage is oversized.  With an easy to maintain yard, this could be the home you have been looking for.
